data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN: 2.75%!!!  Looking for the perfect place to call home and minutes to white sandy beaches, shopping, dining, and entertainment?  Check out this immaculate 4 bedroom, 2 bath smart home located in the highly desirable Venetian Pointe community!  No shutters here - all impact windows!  Featuring a double foyer with large open concept family room, oversize master bath suite with walk-in shower, double sink, and granite vanity.  The gourmet style kitchen has a large quartz peninsula island, perfect for your "inner" chef, stainless steel appliances, and open to the great room.  42" kitchen cabinets with crown molding and under cabinet lighting.  New water heater (2021), reverse osmosis water filtration (2021), and new gutters (2022).  Plumbed for outdoor kitchen.  Plenty of room for a custom pool. All residents enjoy the amenities: large heated pool, cabana area and fitness center.  No CDD and super low HOA fee!  Click the 3D virtual video and schedule your showing today!
